title: Double Tunisian-Spiced Honey Lamb Rump with Sesame Roast Root Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Enjoy the tastes of this Tunisia-inspired dinner that’s sure to transport your taste buds. In one bite you’ll be hit with spiced
succulent lamb drizzled in honey, roasted veggies and punchy garlic yoghurt. Everyone will want seconds!

